, THE COMPANYS STATIN FOR MODIFYING

CHOLESTEROL, AND

PROSCAR

, A UROLOGY PRODUCT FOR THE

TREATMENT OF SYMPTOMATIC BENIGN PROSTATE ENLARGEMENT.

