PARTNERSHIP ARE RECORDED IN EQUITY INCOME FROM AFFILIATES. MERCK

RECOGNIZED EQUITY INCOME OF $1,830.8 MILLION IN 2007,

$1,218.6 MILLION IN 2006 AND $570.4 MILLION IN 2005.

