CREDIT WERE $100 MILLION AND $90 MILLION,

RESPECTIVELY, AND ARE INCLUDED IN LOANS PAYABLE. THE WEIGHTED

AVERAGE INTEREST RATE FOR ALL OF THESE BORROWINGS INCLUDED IN

