RETIREMENT PLANS FOR BREACH OF FIDUCIARY DUTY. THE LAWSUITS MAKE

SIMILAR ALLEGATIONS TO THE ALLEGATIONS CONTAINED IN THE

VIOXX

SECURITIES LAWSUITS. ON JULY 11, 2006, JUDGE CHESLER

